name: Traveling Artist Book traveling through some streets
description:
Traveling Artist Book traveling through some streets

This book was carried out through several walks through the cities of Campinas, Jundiai and São Paulo during the year 2019, as a project "South Realism, Art and the edges of cities" for the completion of the Visual Arts course at the University of Campinas-São Paulo - Brazil.

The images that make up the book are of objects, bus tickets, rust and plants collected and printed on paper through phitography.

Caró - artist book, pg .14/60 - 2019
